# Document System Enhancements Implementation Plan

This plan covers integrating Swagger, adding time-based template versioning, and enhancing the UI template editor according to your requests.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Visual Timeline**: I will build a custom interactive Timeline component using pure React state, HTML, and Tailwind CSS. It will show a graphical bar chart mapping out the time periods of different template versions to fulfill the request for "hiển thị cây thời gian có thể kéo thả...". Dragging the blocks will update the `validFrom`/`validTo` data.
> - **AppClient Template Association**: Currently, the DB schema associates Templates to Owners (Users), but not explicitly to specific AppClients. I will assume we need to join this, or simply list all active templates and let the AppClient "subscribe" to them via a new junction table or just list all templates available if there's no strict scoping wanted yet. I will create a `client_templates` junction table or equivalent if strict scoping is needed, or just list templates in the detail modal.
> Please review and approve this approach for Phase 2!

## Proposed Changes

### API (document-system)
#### [NEW] [package.json](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/package.json) dependencies
- Install `@nestjs/swagger` and `swagger-ui-express`.

#### [MODIFY] [src/main.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/main.ts)
- Setup Swagger UI at `/api/docs`.

#### [MODIFY] [src/templates/entities/template.entity.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/templates/entities/template.entity.ts)
- Add `isTimeBased` (boolean, default false).
- Add `validFrom` (timestamp/Date, nullable).
- Add `validTo` (timestamp/Date, nullable).

#### [MODIFY] [src/templates/templates.service.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/templates/templates.service.ts)
- Add validation in `createVersion` and [update](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/users/users.service.ts#53-56) methods to check for overlapping `validFrom`/`validTo` ranges when `isTimeBased` is true.
- Add logic in [findByCode](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/templates/repositories/templates.repository.ts#45-48) to optionally accept a target Date or version number to resolve the correct version.

#### [MODIFY] [src/generator/generator.controller.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/generator/generator.controller.ts) & [src/templates/templates.controller.ts](file:///C:/Users/kidcher1412/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/document-system/src/templates/templates.controller.ts)
- Extract optional `x-template-version` header.
- Pass header value or current date to the service to resolve the correct template version for rendering.

