## Verification Plan
1. Check that clicking the gear icon in the template editor reveals the interactive version timeline.
2. Ensure dragging blocks in the timeline updates the corresponding dates.
3. Access Dashboard, Users, and AppClients pages to verify real data loads successfully.
4. Open the details view of an AppClient to inspect connection details and template bindings.
